name: Contemporary Plain 925 Sterling Silver Ring Open Cylinder
description:
Surrounded by a border that curls superbly outwards and gently concaved around the middle the open bottom of this Sterling Silver cylinder ring is generously curved and adds a bright silver shine to the looks with its high polished lustrous style. A modern ring, adding a trendy flair to a woman's appearance that sits comfortably on the finger. Hallmarked 925 silver and the contemporary design create a fabulous silver jewellery.
Approx. weight 	4.94 g
Dimensions 	(WxHxD) 21x22x22 mm

name: Handmade Ornate Silver Triple Hinged Sponge Coral Pendant
description:
Handmade ornate Sterling Silver triple hinged Sponge Coral pendant features the round cut, set in silver Sponge Coral stacked and interconnected with hinges to the dainty bail. The three resin glazed coral cabochons are all of the same size and each is embellished with a hand soldered sun flower in the center that is composed of tiny silver beads and surrounded by small circles that are placed diligently one by one by hand. Superb work of artisans that master the art of jewelry making that has a wonderful high fashion flair and looks stunning when showcased on the neckline. Long and graceful coral silver pendant, displays the floral theme in a very own way. Harvesting admiring compliments when the light breaks itself on the beaded centers, beautifully contrasted by the dashing red of the vibrant Sponge Coral. Gorgeous
Approx. weight 	10.65 g
Dimensions 	(WxHxD) 21x80x5 mm
Diameter 	21 mm
